## VRC OSC Utils

A quick and dirty library to interact with VRChat's OSC interface. Includes the following features:

- Bundle messages, created using keyword parameters.

- A watch server to send time messages to your avatar.

## Usage

`python -m vrc_osc_utils [-h] [--port PORT] [--host HOST]

options:
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --port, -p PORT  The UDP port to send OSC messages to.
  --host, -a HOST  The IP address to send OSC Messages to.`
  
`python -m vrc_osc_utils watch [--delay DELAY]
  
options:
   --delay, -d DELAY  The interval delay to send the watch time.`

